%% T40 · Loader lifecycle — load → cache → render → invalidate
%% Created: 2026-06-02
%% Render with any Mermaid 10+ renderer. Dark theme assumed.
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle: Idle\n(cache: empty)
    Loading: Loading\n(single in-flight fetch)
    Cached: Cached\n(cache: Prompt[])
    Rendering: Rendering\n(resolve {{vars}})
    Failed: Failed\n(typed PromptError)

    Idle --> Loading: loadAll()
    Loading --> Cached: store.list() ok\n+ merge defaults/user
    Loading --> Failed: ParseFailed / SchemaInvalid /\nSlugCollision / StoreUnavailable

    Cached --> Rendering: render(slug, ctx)
    Rendering --> Cached: text returned\n(may emit UnresolvedVariable warning)
    Rendering --> Failed: NotFound

    Cached --> Loading: invalidate()\nthen loadAll()
    Cached --> Idle: invalidate()\n(no immediate re-fetch)

    Failed --> Idle: caller handled error\n+ optional retry

    note right of Cached
      Invalidation triggers (T37):
      I1 explicit invalidate()
      I2 store.onChange(saved/deleted/imported)
      I3 fs mtime advanced (fs-backed)
      I4 defaults bundle reloaded
    end note

    note left of Rendering
      Variable precedence (T38):
      1. ctx.vars[name]
      2. ctx.editor.*
      3. ctx.now → date/time/datetime/iso
      4. empty + UnresolvedVariable event
    end note
